    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document retires the use of GOST R 34.10-2001 (mnemonic "ECC-GOST") and GOST R 34.11-94 within DNSSEC.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;RFC 5933 (Historic) defined the use of GOST R 34.10-2001 and GOST R 34.11-94 algorithms with DNS Security Extensions (DNSSEC). This document updates RFC 5933 by deprecating the use of ECC-GOST.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
    </abstract>
